Paper: hep-th/0003293

Date: 2000-03-31

Title: Higher Dimensional Schwinger-like Anomalous Effective Action

Authors: A.Smailagic, E. Spallucci

Comments: 7 pages, no figures, ReVTeX, to appear in Phys.Rev.D

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D62 (2000) 045010

We construct explicit form of the anomalous effective action, in arbitraryeven dimension, for Abelian vector and axial gauge fields coupled to Diracfermions. It turns out to be a surprisingly simple extension of 2D Schwingermodel effective action.